{
  "texts": [
    "3) Directly test our classifier on BigFive Essay.",
    "This experiment aimed to determine whether incorporating the BigFive Essay dataset could enhance classification performance and whether the dataset itself is well-suited for personality classification using the RoBERTa model.",
    "After merging the Psych-Generator dataset with the BigFive Essay dataset, we retrained the classifier and evaluated its performance on the BigFive Essay test set.",
    "However, the results on BigFive Essay testset showed no improvement compared to the original classifier.",
    "Similarly, performance on the PsychGenerator test set remained unchanged, fluctuating between 54% and 58%."
  ]
}